%20didn't%20have%20the%20majority%2C%20we%20had%20140%20seats.%20We%20returned%20to%20power%20in%202009%20with%20209%20seats.%20We%20formed%20the%20UPA%20alliance%20and%20ran%20the%20government%20for%2010%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20even%20wise%20people%20forget%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2081-year-old%20said%2C%20taking%20a%20jibe%20at%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20who%20had%20been%20targeting%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20for%20failing%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20Prime%20Ministerial%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20BJP%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20party%20lied%20to%20the%20country%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20it%20talked%20about%202%20crore%20jobs%20in%202014%2C%20when%20it%20talked%20about%20reducing%20inflation.%20Nothing%20happened%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20made%20big%20promises%20in%202014%20and%202019%20but%20did%20not%20look%20back%20after%20that.%20He%20did%20not%20help%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20when%20it%20was%20struck%20by%20a%20natural%20disaster.%20The%20BJP%20is%20working%20to%20topple%20governments%20in%20the%20country%20and%20has%20tried%20to%20destabilise%20the%20Congress%20government%20of%20Himachal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2027%2C%20six%20former%20Congress%20MLAs%20-%20Rajinder%20Rana%20(Sujanpur)%2C%20Sudhir%20Sharma%20(Dharamshala)%2C%20Ravi%20Thakur%20(Lahaul%20and%20Spiti)%2C%20Inder%20Dutt%20Lakhanpal%20(Barsar)%2C%20Chetanya%20Sharma%20(Gagret)%20and%20Devinder%20Kumar%20Bhutto%20(Kutlehar)%20-%20had%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20nominee%20Harsh%20Mahajan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20they%20were%20disqualified%20for%20defying%20a%20party%20whip%20to%20be%20present%20in%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20and%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20government%20during%20the%20cut%20motions%20and%20budget.%20These%20MLAs%20later%20joined%20the%20BJP%20and%20were%20given%20the%20ticket%20from%20t