n%20over%20400%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh's%20comment%20comes%20on%20a%20day%20people%20voted%20in%20the%20sixth%20of%20the%20seven-phase%20elections.%20The%20last%20round%20of%20voting%20will%20be%20held%20on%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20well%20as%20other%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20also%20been%20saying%20the%20party%20will%20cross%20400%20seats%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B400%20paar%20(crossing%20400)%20was%20not%20just%20our%20campaign%20slogan%2C%20but%20our%20resolve.%20After%20six%20phases%2C%20we%20are%20very%20confident%20of%20crossing%20that%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20told%20NDTV%20on%20May%2012%20during%20a%20roadshow%20in%20Bihar%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20expand%20its%20footprint%20hugely%20in%20eastern%20India%20this%20time%2C%20which%20would%20take%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20easily%20over%20the%20400-seat%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20visited%20almost%20all%20the%20states%20of%20India.%20And%20I%20can%20say%20that%20Bihar%20has%20added%20many%20colours%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20NDA's%20resolution%20of%20'400%20paar'.%20The%20atmosphere%20in%20Bihar%20is%20the%20same%20as%20that%20of%20the%20entire%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20contested%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Lucknow%20constituency%20this%20time%20again.%20He%20had%20won%20from%20there%20twice.%20Lucknow%20is%20a%20prestigious%20seat%20previously%20represented%20by%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20BJP%20retained%20power%20in%202019%2C%20with%20an%20even%20larger%20seat%20share%20than%20in%202014.%20Mr%20Singh%20remained%20one%20of%20the%20key%20members%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20cabinet%20and%20was%20given%20charge%20of%20the%20Defence%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20in%20mind%20the%20spirit%20of%20'Make%20in%20India'%20and%20'Aatmanirbhar%20Bharat'%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20banned%20the%20import%20of%20101%20defence-related%20items%20in%202020.%20In%20May%202021%2C%20he%20decided%20that%20108%20military%20weapons%20and%20systems%2C%20including%20next-generation%20corvettes%2C%20airborne%20early%20warning%20systems%2C%20tank%20engines%20and%20radars%20would%20be%20entirely%20made%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716647580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fm9u10b1_rajnath-singh_625x300_25_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-400-paar-not-just-a-campaign-slogan-but-rajnath-singh-to-ndtv-5744322%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20has%20expressed%20confidence%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20will%20win%20over%20400%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20this%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-400-paar-not-just-a-campaign-slogan-but-rajnath-singh-to-ndtv-5744322%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-400-paar-not-just-a-campaign-slogan-but-rajnath-singh-to-ndtv-5744322%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-400-paar-not-just-a-campaign-slogan-but-rajnath-singh-to-ndtv-5744322%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Uses%20Voice-Changing%20App%20To%20Pose%20As%20Woman%20Professor%2C%20Rapes%207%20Students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20illiterate%2C%20but%20that%20didn't%20stop%20him%20from%C2%A0leveraging%20technology%20to%20commit%20a%20string%20of%20heinous%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20an%20app%20to%20morph%20his%20voice%2C%20Brajesh%20Kushwaha%2C%20a%20former%20mill%20worker%2C%20would%20pose%20as%20a%20woman%20teacher%