t%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20headed%20for%20a%20defeat%20in%20the%20ongoing%20general%20election%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20results%20are%20out%2C%20RJD%20and%20Congress%20workers%20will%20be%20seen%20tearing%20off%20each%20other's%20clothes.%20The%20royal%20family%20of%20the%20Congress%20will%20put%20the%20entire%20blame%20of%20defeat%20on%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20leave%20for%20holiday%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20said%20no%20Prime%20Minister%20would%20have%20used%20such%20language.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20Modiji%20saying%3F%20Is%20it%20not%20his%20responsibility%20to%20maintain%20the%20decorum%20of%20his%20post%3F%20We%20respect%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20post.%20His%20reality%20can%20now%20be%20seen.%20Do%20not%20show%20so%20much%20reality%20to%20the%20country.%20He%20has%20forgotten%20that%20he%20represents%20the%20country.%20What%20will%20the%20future%20generations%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20with%20ally%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Gorakhpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20over%20his%20allegation%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20planning%20a%20wealth%20redistribution%20scheme%20under%20which%20women's%20mangalsutras%20will%20be%20snatched%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20some%20days%2C%20Modiji%20talks%20about%20buffaloes%20and%20on%20other%20days%2C%20he%20talks%20about%20mangalsutra.%20The%20problem%20of%20stray%20animals%20began%20in%20their%20term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20it%20is%20the%20BJP's%20candidates%20who%20are%20going%20around%20claiming%20that%20the%20party%20will%20change%20the%20Constitution%20if%20it%20returns%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticising%20the%20%26quot%3Bmujra%26quot%3B%20remark%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20said%20that%20with%20each%20phase%20of%20the%20election