om%2Fentertainment%2Fstranger-things-star-millie-bobby-brown-is-now-married-to-fiance-jon-bon-jovi-details-inside-5743300%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPattern%20In%20Creating%20False%20Narratives%26quot%3B%3A%20Poll%20Body%20Amid%20Voter%20Turnout%20Data%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20today%20released%20the%20absolute%20number%20of%20voters%20for%20all%20the%20completed%20phases%20-%20six%20of%20the%20seven%20phases%20-%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%202024.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20EC%20also%20said%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bnoted%20a%20pattern%20of%20false%20narratives%20and%20mischievous%20design%20to%20vitiate%20the%20electoral%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20statement%20came%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20adjourned%20-%20till%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20-%20petitions%20seeking%20release%20of%20voter%20turnout%20data%2C%20including%20votes%20polled%20and%2For%20rejected%2C%20within%2048%20hours%20of%20end%20of%20polling%20at%20each%20booth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitions%20had%20sought%20directions%20to%20the%20EC%20to%20compile%20and%20publish%20this%20data%20on%20its%20website%20after%20each%20phase%2C%20beginning%20with%20the%20next%20round%20of%20voting%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20feels%20duly%20strengthened%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20observations%20and%20verdict%20on%20the%20process%20of%20release%20of%20turnout%20data%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20today%20while%20voting%20was%20going%20on%20in%20the%20sixth%20phase.%20The%20final%20phase%20is%20on%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20brings%20upon%20the%20Commission%2C%20a%20higher%20responsibility%20to%20serve%20the%20cause%20of%20electoral%20democracy%20with%20undeterred%20resolution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%