2Fhow-it-works%5C%22%3Eofficial%20site%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20from%20the%20check-in%20point%2C%20the%20BARK%20Air%20concierge%20will%20welcome%20all%20the%20pets%20and%20help%20them%20settle%20in%20the%20dog-centric%20cabins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20never%20book%20to%20their%20full%20capacity%20to%20ensure%20you%20and%20your%20dog%20have%20enough%20room%20to%20spread%20out%20comfortably.%E2%80%9D%20That's%20not%20all!%20These%20dog-centric%20cabins%20are%20specially%20prepped%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20calming%20aids%20such%20as%20pheromone%2C%20music%2C%20warm%20lavender%20scented%20refreshment%20towels%2C%20and%20other%20comforts%20to%20help%20each%20dog%20feel%20settled.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWait%20there%20is%20more.%20Each%20of%20the%20concierge%20on%20the%20flight%20carries%20a%20%E2%80%9C'just%20in%20case'%20bag%20filled%20with%20calming%20treats%2C%20leashes%2C%20poop%20bags%2C%20and%20more%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fair.bark.co%2Fpages%2Fhow-it-works%5C%22%3Esite%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadded%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20onboard%2C%20dogs%20will%20be%20served%20their%20beverage%20of%20choice%20(water%2C%20bone%20broth%2C%20you%20name%20it)%2C%20during%20ascent%20and%20descent%20to%20ensure%20they%20do%20not%20experience%20any%20ear%20discomfort%20commonly%20caused%20by%20the%20change%20in%20cabin%20pressure.%20In%20addition%2C%20a%20variety%20of%20BARK-branded%20treats%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20surprises%20will%20be%20served%20throughout%20the%20flight%20experience.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fswirlster.ndtv.com%2Ftravel%2Ftravel-to-this-jeffersonville-vermont-farm-in-usa-to-play-pet-and-hang-out-with-a-gang-of-golden-retrievers-dogs-5187708%5C%22%3ETravel%20To%20This%20Vermont%20Farm%20In%20USA%20To%20Play%2C%20Pet%20And%20Hang%20Out%20With%20A%20Gang%20Of%20Golden%20Retrievers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716620760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22