ess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Have%20faith%20and%20self-belief%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaith%20and%20self-belief%20are%20essential%20for%20starting%20any%20business.%20When%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20struck%20in%202020%2C%20Raji%20Sakthi%20from%20Kerala%2C%20like%20many%20others%2C%20did%20not%20lose%20hope.%20With%20strong%20support%20from%20her%20husband%20and%20children%2C%20she%20secured%20a%20gold%20loan%20and%20embarked%20on%20her%20cloud%20kitchen%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20started%20her%20venture%20under%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98From%20the%20Kitchen%20%E2%80%94%20Homely%20Foods%E2%80%99%20and%20never%20looked%20back.%20She%20now%20gets%20at%20least%20100%20orders%20per%20week!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Start%20with%20small%20investments%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Raji%2C%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20smaller%20investments%20translate%20to%20smaller%20risks.%20Coming%20from%20a%20humble%20background%2C%20she%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CInvest%20a%20minimal%20amount%20in%20the%20sector.%20Always%20keep%20these%20two%20points%20in%20mind%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20small%20homegrown%20business%2C%20so%20it%20takes%20time%20to%20see%20better%20results%2C%20and%20never%20expect%20to%20make%20a%20profit%20in%20a%20month%20or%20two.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Know%20your%20market%20and%20consumers%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConduct%20market%20research%2C%20analyse%20competitors%2C%20and%20gather%20feedback%20to%20alter%20your%20menu%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20pricing%20for%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%2C%20consider%20factors%20such%20as%20ingredient%20costs%2C%20labour%2C%20overhead%20expenses%2C%20market%20demand%2C%20and%20perceived%20value.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20profitability%20and%20affordability%20while%20ensuring%20the%20quality%20of%20your%20