E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20limited%20vacancies%20for%20government%20jobs%20and%20there%20is%20too%20much%20competition%20in%20this%20field.%20Anyway%2C%20I%20appeared%20for%20many%20state%20and%20central-level%20examinations%20in%20February%202020%20but%20I%20did%20not%20get%20any%20results.%20I%20was%20sitting%20idle%20for%20at%20least%20six%20months%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do%20and%20was%20just%20waiting%20for%20my%20results.%20I%20was%20getting%20demotivated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202021%2C%20his%20father%20read%20about%20the%20donkey-rearing%20business%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20concept%20was%20not%20at%20all%20popularised%20in%20the%20North.%20Although%20there%20is%20little%20demand%20for%20donkey%20milk%20in%20the%20country%2C%20it%20has%20huge%20demand%20in%20countries%20like%20Turkey%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20China%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20a%20time%20when%20people%20are%20bothered%20by%20soaring%20prices%20of%20cow%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173064%2Fmilk-cow-camel-almond-coconut-yak-goat-soy-coconut-alternative-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuffaloes%20milk%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20Rs%2060%20per%20litre%2C%20they%20are%20not%20interested%20in%20buying%20donkey%20milk%20which%20is%20sold%20for%20Rs%203%2C500%20a%20litre.%20But%20it%20has%20an%20international%20market%20and%20is%20widely%20used%20in%20pharmaceutical%20and%20cosmetics%20industries%20to%20make%20products%20like%20moisturisers%2C%20baby%20cream%2C%20and%20soaps%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7555024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2020%20research%20article%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereveals%20that%20donkey%20milk%20stimulates%20the%20immune%20system%2C%20regulates%2